    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1286280/extras/e00b00400e819531d3ef3eeb56dbdc89.avif?t=1745476379\" width=600 height=150 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >类银河恶魔城经典玩法</h2>-穿梭在 9 大风格迥异的区域地图中，灵活运用多种能力解决谜题、挑战强敌<br>-41 种技能道具，助力新兵波弟成长为强大的守护者<br>-60 多种变异海洋怪物，带来惊险刺激的战斗体验<br>-更有多篇剧情动画以及遍布各个角落的趣味彩蛋，众多探索元素等你来体验<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >零重力的冒险之旅</h2>在《弃海》世界中，玩家将从重力的束缚中解放出来，在庞大的深海世界中向任意方向自由移动。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1286280/extras/9e27a5256dc1e61305fda99d6929c594.avif?t=1745476379\" width=600 height=70 /></span><br>陨石灾难、极端气候……在未来，人类不得不避居海底，建立起一片拥有数百座海底都市的现代亚特兰蒂斯。然而，受海洋垃圾污染的变异怪物们，正逐渐侵吞着人类的生存空间……身为守护者的“波弟”及仿生剑鱼“勃朗特”将在庞大的深海世界中与入侵者展开激战，并在冒险旅程中逐步揭开隐藏在深海都市“罗伊拉”背后的秘密。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1286280/extras/7177da4766a1b20514d4baa8f034f18f.avif?t=1745476379\" width=600 height=70 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >双线配合的特殊战斗系统</h2>守护者“波弟”熟知战术但需注意保护自身，仿生剑鱼“勃朗特”免疫伤害但需听从指令战斗，最佳拍档联手对敌，带来独特的战斗手感。在移动“波弟”闪避攻击的同时，操控 “勃朗特”向敌人发起进攻。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1286280/extras/2b562e70b96b0de6934950494a42e119.poster.avif?t=1745476379\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1286280/extras/2b562e70b96b0de6934950494a42e119.webm?t=1745476379\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1286280/extras/2b562e70b96b0de6934950494a42e119.mp4?t=1745476379\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >凶狠诡异的海洋垃圾变异鱼</h2>从浑身利刃的嗜血千刃鲨，到凶残神秘的大洋罗刹，在冒险旅程中，波弟与勃朗特将遭遇大量极具风格和威慑力的深海巨怪，击退这些凶猛的入侵者，拯救海底都市的未来！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1286280/extras/d78d4714b92a520cdaa2b35e8d7902ba.poster.avif?t=1745476379\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1286280/extras/d78d4714b92a520cdaa2b35e8d7902ba.webm?t=1745476379\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1286280/extras/d78d4714b92a520cdaa2b35e8d7902ba.mp4?t=1745476379\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >丰富的技能策略组合</h2>危机四伏的深海都市中潜藏着无数致命的威胁，为“波弟”植入各式各样的记忆板，在众多技能效果中进行取舍，打造专属的战斗风格、应对守护者之路上的一切阻碍。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1286280/extras/0d82e7a488dcc7d2804a61d834310407.poster.avif?t=1745476379\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1286280/extras/0d82e7a488dcc7d2804a61d834310407.webm?t=1745476379\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1286280/extras/0d82e7a488dcc7d2804a61d834310407.mp4?t=1745476379\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >身临其境的海底冒险</h2>游戏采用色彩艳丽、线条简洁的手绘美术风格，配合沉浸式的海底背景音乐，营造出神秘又诡谲多变的深海城市氛围。肃穆的妈祖神像、恢弘的海底壁画……与波弟一起，在深海废墟中探寻人类文明曾经的辉煌。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1286280/extras/d45f8720d4799e73fb6a1399154d55cf.poster.avif?t=1745476379\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1286280/extras/d45f8720d4799e73fb6a1399154d55cf.webm?t=1745476379\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1286280/extras/d45f8720d4799e73fb6a1399154d55cf.mp4?t=1745476379\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FOLLOW US ON DISCORD</h2>",
